---
title: Seared Pork Chops with Plum Compote, Garlic Swiss Chard and Wild Rice
description: Plums are the perfect autumn fruit. Very sweet, a little tart, and all kinds of delicious. We're cooking them up with a bit of brown sugar, cinnamon and vinegar to make a delightful sauce for your pork chops!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/seared-pork-chops-9b31c77e.jpg
